OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FRain will spread across western areas
OL,8,Fduring the early hours, but remaining
OL,9,Fdry across the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FRain spreading east through
OL,12,Fthe morning. Drier with bright spells
OL,13,Fin the afternoon along with a few
OL,14,Fshowers, these turning heavy in the
OL,15,Fwest later. Colder than of late.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,18,Fsome sunshine on Friday, outbreaks of
OL,19,Frain spreading northeast in the
OL,20,Fevening. Mainly dry on Saturday.
OL,21,FBreezy with showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
